So with some coaxing…ok with a LOT of nagging from my team, I present to you my delicious Spinach Artichoke Dip Christmas Tree bread thing

Ingredients:

1/4 cup Artichoke
Shredded mozarella
1 cup of Spinach 
Garlic powder
Sour cream
Mayonnaise 
Pillsbury pizza dough

Make the dip by placing diced artichoke, spinach and garlic in a pan until cooked
Place 1/4 cup of sour cream, a dollop of mayonnaise and a 1/4 cup of mozzarella cheese until cream and cheese has melted through
Mix together
OR buy your favorite spinach artichoke dip in your local grocery store
